{"tid":2148871,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【推上熱門】一人一蘋果行動：#WeNeedAppleDaily","createTime":"2020-08-10T06:34:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-10T09:06:01.000Z","uid":126626,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"bcdc1419af2eff84061a64b5c405f8b20cad8e75","tid":2148871,"uid":126626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T06:34:23.000Z","msg":"Source：Terry媒體懶人堂<br />\n買爆毒果！！！Twitter打國際線！！！！<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"gold\">【一人一蘋果Challenge：#WeNeedAppleDaily】<br />\n<br />\n好多網民呼籲，聽日《蘋果》出白紙都要買爆。無限感激。<br />\n<br />\n任何方法，盡量喺本地同國際聲援蘋果日報。<br />\n<br />\n作為蘋果前員工，我發起【一人一蘋果Challenge】，希望各位香港人響應🙏￼￼<br />\n<br />\n今日聽日，一人買一份《蘋果》紙本，影相放上所有社交平台，包括FB、IG、Twitter等等。<br />\n<br />\n加一個Hashtag：#WeNeedAppleDaily<br />\n<br />\n唔知聽日A1會點設計，但希望各位盡力支持。世上所有事情，都唔係理所當然。<br />\n<br />\n今日有心人狂掃壹傳媒股票撐黎智英，帳面意外勁賺。就算是商業市場，都會有無法預料的好人好事。<br />\n<br />\n一人一蘋果，We Need Apple Daily。</span></span><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8Dm4Yd4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8Dm4Yd4.png&h=a6df68ac&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"efd2359b6fd84835485a3eafc04bcede4c8a924d","tid":2148871,"uid":126626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T06:34:43.000Z","msg":"推推推，Gphone都支持左！"},{"pid":"d6ad7f5b9e85e5c618e83bb22f1b3aa120221964","tid":2148871,"uid":331590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T06:34:49.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"a6ba56e1ea8fce0f834a11a402b85687f25d43f6","tid":2148871,"uid":60358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T06:35:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c67ff5ece5dad59e657691908ae3f52b2c45d462","tid":2148871,"uid":127929,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T06:35:48.000Z","msg":"一人一手買蘋果(00282)<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fa